<p class="">Order. The right hon. Gentleman the Leader of the Opposition gives way.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-aaea786d-875e-4d21-84c9-c8993a36cd0a" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
