<p class="">What happens if we are left alone?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-ef6ab15c-dd82-44cb-ac9e-a3c3c8214790" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
