                Mr. George Griffiths
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-2a73728c-5801-4c09-a1ae-1fdc7c8ff71b" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
